<h2>Basis</h2>

<p>The Pieuvre is a RSS feed aggregator.</p>

<h3>Feed</h3> 

<p>is what we call a RSS feed, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/RSS">more at Wikipedia.</a></p>

<h3>Follow/Unfollow</h3>

<p>are the action of adding or removing RSS feeds.</p>
<h3>Article</h3>

<p>is a single news from a RSS feed.</p>
<h3>Member</h3>

<p>is a registered user on the Pieuvre. Members can follow all RSS feeds they like.</p>

